{"tid":584021,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"『傑出阿宅系列』保護File套既File套開箱","createTime":"2018-03-07T13:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T13:52:21.000Z","uid":25250,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a81d27460a53b913accf492926a59c72f76c9b3","tid":584021,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"相信各位傑出既阿宅都同我一樣，會有一堆file套<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/211900_2df563abc73c0550e4529be81b6a2969.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F211900_2df563abc73c0550e4529be81b6a2969.png&h=2fffccb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近我係amazon買左呢樣野 700yen 20個套<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/212042_232c8a597e0f7d5333908bd90ea2c6ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F212042_232c8a597e0f7d5333908bd90ea2c6ae.png&h=cb40df7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身D File套外面有個套 我就唔拆直接放埋入去 即係同時有兩個套保護緊個file套<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/212153_c3bb5dcaed25af73f825ef010025e0d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F212153_c3bb5dcaed25af73f825ef010025e0d2.png&h=baa6fd7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\namazon介紹個度寫20個套可以放到40個file套 但係我發現我有D套係前後唔同畫像 即係放唔足四十個<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/212437_7432f31fcbd31915650b5e820a9953fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F212437_7432f31fcbd31915650b5e820a9953fd.png&h=a022792d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/212438_206eb3cdde02225d3ea01300688a5452.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F212438_206eb3cdde02225d3ea01300688a5452.png&h=96049c42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附贈 原來有D套會過高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/212421_f2e8730d7cd86440b5b2c23c7f2c492c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F212421_f2e8730d7cd86440b5b2c23c7f2c492c.png&h=9c695fc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13bfaaeb796a12ec6ef4c0f6ccdc9bf396b3b288","tid":584021,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:37:56.000Z","msg":"_登已經唔係毒撚論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa65425a1453c08834d06454d08989c491063583","tid":584021,"uid":3342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"死毒撚好嘔心<br />\nFile都要安全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179d53b2d2d9c1f0d3bc5170d44a7c55e6bc1ccc","tid":584021,"uid":2223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"套住file套嘅file套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330a59fe13e5c407869d4c8c19a56fa3ded80e7f","tid":584021,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"aa65425a1453c08834d06454d08989c491063583","tid":584021,"uid":3342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:45:17.000Z","msg":"死毒撚好嘔心<br />\nFile都要安全套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"唔記得左呢度係5P登，以為上緊毒撚登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}